ENABLE_IMAGES - bool. Enables images format in telegram bot
FONTS_PATH - path to fonts for tg images. Example "/usr/src/app/data/helvetica_bold.ttf"

IMAGE_HEIGHT - int. Default - 0.5
IMAGE_WIDTH - int. Default - 0.5
IMAGE_TEXT_Y - float64. Default - 0.5
IMAGE_TEXT_WITH_ADDITIONAL_Y - float64. Y of main text if additional text set. Default 0.6
IMAGE_ADDITIONAL_TEXT_Y - float64. Default - 0.2
IMAGE_TEXT_WIDTH - float64. Relative to width. Default - 0.8
IMAGE_TEXT_FONT_SIZE - int. Default - 50
IMAGE_ADDITIONAL_TEXT_FONT_SIZE - int. Default - 45
IS_DUMB_SHUFFLE - bool. If enabled - disables decks shuffling according to table used_questions - uses just rand question from selected level